texts.orig: I've tested this Debian etch to lenny upgrade process a few times so far, and it seems to be working well.
texts.text: I've tested this Debian etch to lenny upgrade process a few times so far, and it seems to be working well.

texts.label: code
texts.orig:
sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list     [change 'etch' -> 'lenny']
sudo aptitude update
sudo aptitude install apt dpkg aptitude
sudo aptitude full-upgrade
texts.text:
sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list     [change 'etch' -> 'lenny']
sudo aptitude update
sudo aptitude install apt dpkg aptitude
sudo aptitude full-upgrade
